    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/fb954ca8882b9469b9463a9c5a7145ef.poster.avif?t=1760700212\" width=352 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/fb954ca8882b9469b9463a9c5a7145ef.webm?t=1760700212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/fb954ca8882b9469b9463a9c5a7145ef.mp4?t=1760700212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/e8caf98de4c446eb8efee68ce49c67e7.webp?t=1760700212\" width=480 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accompany agent <strong>Steph</strong>, right hand of the revered forbidden flower, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >on the hunt for their final rival residing in the beautiful and glamorous </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >casino, the <strong>Casa De Diamantes</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/d97a12fe9e877d2037d51c2558215d54.poster.avif?t=1760700212\" width=480 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/d97a12fe9e877d2037d51c2558215d54.webm?t=1760700212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Casa De Diamantes</strong> is a <strong>2D movement shooter</strong> with aggressive enemy </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >encounters and tight level design. Fight your way through multiple enemy </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >types, collect chips then spend and gamble them away at the casino. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play blackjack, customize your appearance and upgrade your arsenal </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >at the Casa De Diamantes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/7ce5716f5d46efa93cdcc72a9260e1e7.poster.avif?t=1760700212\" width=696 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/7ce5716f5d46efa93cdcc72a9260e1e7.webm?t=1760700212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/7ce5716f5d46efa93cdcc72a9260e1e7.mp4?t=1760700212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/5305e12b881a9582a70025cbbb4ad942.poster.avif?t=1760700212\" width=8 height=8 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/5305e12b881a9582a70025cbbb4ad942.webm?t=1760700212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> Momentum Based Movement</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/5305e12b881a9582a70025cbbb4ad942.poster.avif?t=1760700212\" width=8 height=8 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394970/extras/5305e12b881a9582a70025cbbb4ad942.webm?t=1760700212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> Dangerous Enemies wi